---
// Design V1: Warm Studio
// Light, warm, human-centred. DM Serif Display + DM Sans. Terracotta + sage.
---

<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>DTP — Warm Studio Concept</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Sans:ital,opsz,wght@0,9..40,300;0,9..40,400;0,9..40,500;0,9..40,600;1,9..40,400&family=DM+Serif+Display&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
</head>
<body>
  <!-- Navigation -->
  <nav class="ws-nav">
    <div class="ws-container ws-nav-inner">
      <a href="/design-v1" class="ws-logo">Digital Technology Partner</a>
      <div class="ws-nav-links">
        <a href="/design-v1">Home</a>
        <a href="#approach">Our Approach</a>
        <a href="#work">Case Studies</a>
        <a href="#faq">FAQ</a>
        <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
      </div>
      <a href="https://outlook.office.com/bookwithme/user/f0762b9af6a94ed2add9818a4f3ca4e5@digitaltechnologypartner.ai/meetingtype/qc2lOXjEdkO6GkMS_jZJrQ2?anonymous" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="ws-btn ws-btn-primary ws-nav-cta">Book a Call</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="ws-hero">
    <div class="ws-hero-grain"></div>
    <div class="ws-container">
      <div class="ws-hero-content">
        <p class="ws-overline">Aberdeen-based AI consultancy</p>
        <h1>AI that works,<br/><span class="ws-accent">simplified.</span></h1>
        <p class="ws-hero-sub">We cut through the hype, build AI that delivers, and prove value through real results — fast, focused, and tailored to you.</p>
        <div class="ws-hero-actions">
          <a href="https://outlook.office.com/bookwithme/user/f0762b9af6a94ed2add9818a4f3ca4e5@digitaltechnologypartner.ai/meetingtype/qc2lOXjEdkO6GkMS_jZJrQ2?anonymous" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="ws-btn ws-btn-primary">Book a Discovery Call</a>
          <a href="#approach" class="ws-btn ws-btn-ghost">See How We Work →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="ws-hero-dot-grid"></div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Work With Us -->
  <section class="ws-section ws-section-cream" id="benefits">
    <div class="ws-container">
      <h2 class="ws-section-title">Why organisations work with us</h2>
      <div class="ws-benefits-grid">
        <div class="ws-benefit-card">
          <div class="ws-benefit-icon ws-icon-terracotta">
            <svg width="28" height="28" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 9v3.75m-9.303 3.376c-.866 1.5.217 3.374 1.948 3.374h14.71c1.73 0 2.813-1.874 1.948-3.374L13.949 3.378c-.866-1.5-3.032-1.5-3.898 0L2.697 16.126zM12 15.75h.007v.008H12v-.008z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Reduced Risk</h3>
          <p>We deliver in stages. You see progress early and avoid big-bang surprises.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="ws-benefit-card">
          <div class="ws-benefit-icon ws-icon-sage">
            <svg width="28" height="28" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75m-3-7.036A11.959 11.959 0 013.598 6 11.99 11.99 0 003 9.749c0 5.592 3.824 10.29 9 11.623 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.623 0-1.31-.21-2.571-.598-3.751h-.152c-3.196 0-6.1-1.248-8.25-3.285z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Security by Design</h3>
          <p>Data protection and access controls are built in from day one.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="ws-benefit-card">
          <div class="ws-benefit-icon ws-icon-terracotta">
            <svg width="28" height="28" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Reliable Delivery</h3>
          <p>Clear scope, fixed steps, and regular check-ins keep work on track.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="ws-benefit-card">
          <div class="ws-benefit-icon ws-icon-sage">
            <svg width="28" height="28" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.75 3.75v4.5m0-4.5h4.5m-4.5 0L9 9M3.75 20.25v-4.5m0 4.5h4.5m-4.5 0L9 15M20.25 3.75h-4.5m4.5 0v4.5m0-4.5L15 9m5.25 11.25h-4.5m4.5 0v-4.5m0 4.5L15 15"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Scales with You</h3>
          <p>Start small, prove value, then roll out without rework.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="ws-benefit-card">
          <div class="ws-benefit-icon ws-icon-terracotta">
            <svg width="28" height="28" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M10.5 6h9.75M10.5 6a1.5 1.5 0 11-3 0m3 0a1.5 1.5 0 10-3 0M3.75 6H7.5m3 12h9.75m-9.75 0a1.5 1.5 0 01-3 0m3 0a1.5 1.5 0 00-3 0m-3.75 0H7.5m9-6h3.75m-3.75 0a1.5 1.5 0 01-3 0m3 0a1.5 1.5 0 00-3 0m-9.75 0h9.75"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Flexible Engagement</h3>
          <p>On your stack, in our cloud, or a hybrid — whatever fits policy and cost.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="ws-benefit-card">
          <div class="ws-benefit-icon ws-icon-sage">
            <svg width="28" height="28" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.19 8.688a4.5 4.5 0 011.242 7.244l-4.5 4.5a4.5 4.5 0 01-6.364-6.364l1.757-1.757m13.35-.622l1.757-1.757a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364l-4.5 4.5a4.5 4.5 0 001.242 7.244"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Works With Your Tools</h3>
          <p>We integrate with common meeting, messaging, and project platforms.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Testimonial Strip -->
  <section class="ws-section ws-section-white">
    <div class="ws-container ws-testimonial-strip">
      <blockquote>
        <p>"DTP understood our problem within the first meeting. The staged approach meant we could prove value to the board before committing to a full rollout."</p>
        <cite>— Operations Director, Manufacturing</cite>
      </blockquote>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What We Fix -->
  <section class="ws-section ws-section-cream" id="approach">
    <div class="ws-container">
      <h2 class="ws-section-title">What we're asked to fix most often</h2>
      <div class="ws-use-cases">
        <div class="ws-use-card">
          <span class="ws-use-number">01</span>
          <h3>Operations Automation</h3>
          <p>Remove manual steps, reduce errors, and speed up routine work with intelligent process automation.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="ws-use-card">
          <span class="ws-use-number">02</span>
          <h3>Data &amp; Reporting</h3>
          <p>Bring data together and give teams clear dashboards, alerts, and actionable insights.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="ws-use-card">
          <span class="ws-use-number">03</span>
          <h3>AI Assistants for Teams</h3>
          <p>Turn meetings and messages into organised tasks, updates, and automated workflows.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Development Journey -->
  <section class="ws-section ws-section-white" id="process">
    <div class="ws-container">
      <h2 class="ws-section-title">Our 5-stage development process</h2>
      <p class="ws-section-subtitle">Every engagement follows a structured sequence designed to reduce risk and ensure reliable results.</p>
      <div class="ws-journey">
        <div class="ws-journey-step">
          <div class="ws-step-marker">1</div>
          <h3>Discovery</h3>
          <p>Understand your challenge, map existing processes, identify the highest-value opportunity.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="ws-journey-connector"></div>
        <div class="ws-journey-step">
          <div class="ws-step-marker">2</div>
          <h3>Proof of Concept</h3>
          <p>Build a focused prototype to validate the approach and demonstrate feasibility.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="ws-journey-connector"></div>
        <div class="ws-journey-step">
          <div class="ws-step-marker">3</div>
          <h3>MVP</h3>
          <p>Develop a working product with core features ready for real-world testing.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="ws-journey-connector"></div>
        <div class="ws-journey-step">
          <div class="ws-step-marker">4</div>
          <h3>Pilot</h3>
          <p>Deploy with a controlled group, gather feedback, and refine before wider rollout.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="ws-journey-connector"></div>
        <div class="ws-journey-step">
          <div class="ws-step-marker">5</div>
          <h3>Full Launch</h3>
          <p>Scale to production with monitoring, support, and continuous improvement.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Case Studies Preview -->
  <section class="ws-section ws-section-cream" id="work">
    <div class="ws-container">
      <h2 class="ws-section-title">Recent work</h2>
      <div class="ws-cases-grid">
        <div class="ws-case-card">
          <span class="ws-case-tag">Manufacturing</span>
          <h3>Automating Surface Area Calculations for Protective Coatings</h3>
          <p>Transformed hours of manual PDF analysis into minutes with 100% calculation accuracy. OCR-enabled tagging interface with automated Excel report generation.</p>
          <div class="ws-case-metrics">
            <span>Hours → Minutes</span>
            <span>100% Accuracy</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="ws-case-card">
          <span class="ws-case-tag">Manufacturing</span>
          <h3>Intelligent Maintenance Management via Mobile Messaging</h3>
          <p>Messaging-native AI agent for production floor engineers. Natural language processing, voice notes, and photo capture — zero missed maintenance windows.</p>
          <div class="ws-case-metrics">
            <span>Zero Missed Tasks</span>
            <span>No Training Needed</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="ws-case-card">
          <span class="ws-case-tag">Infrastructure</span>
          <h3>AI/ML Expertise as Technical Subcontractor</h3>
          <p>Delivered vector database architecture, ML pipelines, and conversational AI as part of a consultancy's infrastructure monitoring project.</p>
          <div class="ws-case-metrics">
            <span>Expanded Capabilities</span>
            <span>Accelerated Delivery</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ Mini -->
  <section class="ws-section ws-section-white" id="faq">
    <div class="ws-container ws-faq">
      <h2 class="ws-section-title">Common questions</h2>
      <div class="ws-faq-list">
        <details class="ws-faq-item">
          <summary>How long does a typical engagement take?</summary>
          <p>Discovery takes 1–2 weeks. A Proof of Concept typically follows in 4–6 weeks. The full timeline depends on scope, but our staged approach means you see results early.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="ws-faq-item">
          <summary>Do you work with existing systems?</summary>
          <p>Yes. We integrate with your current tools, platforms, and data sources. We're stack-agnostic and work with whatever fits your infrastructure and policies.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="ws-faq-item">
          <summary>What industries do you work with?</summary>
          <p>We've delivered solutions across manufacturing, infrastructure, energy, and professional services. Our process applies to any sector where AI can streamline operations or unlock data.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="ws-faq-item">
          <summary>How is pricing structured?</summary>
          <p>Each stage is priced independently so you can validate value before committing to the next. No big-bang contracts — you stay in control throughout.</p>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="ws-section ws-cta-section" id="contact">
    <div class="ws-container ws-cta-inner">
      <h2>Ready to see what AI can do for your business?</h2>
      <p>Book a free discovery call. We'll listen, assess fit, and outline next steps — no obligation.</p>
      <a href="https://outlook.office.com/bookwithme/user/f0762b9af6a94ed2add9818a4f3ca4e5@digitaltechnologypartner.ai/meetingtype/qc2lOXjEdkO6GkMS_jZJrQ2?anonymous" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="ws-btn ws-btn-primary ws-btn-lg">Book a Discovery Call</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer class="ws-footer">
    <div class="ws-container ws-footer-inner">
      <p>&copy; 2025 Digital Technology Partner. All Rights Reserved.</p>
      <div class="ws-footer-links">
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/dtp-ai/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">LinkedIn</a>
        <a href="mailto:Info@digitaltechnologypartner.ai">Email</a>
        <a href="https://wa.me/447769386204">WhatsApp</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <!-- Design Variant Badge -->
  <div class="ws-variant-badge">
    V1: Warm Studio
    <a href="/design-v2">Next →</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>

<style is:global>
  /* ========== V1: WARM STUDIO ========== */
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  :root {
    --ws-white: #FAFAF8;
    --ws-cream: #F5EDE3;
    --ws-black: #1A1A1A;
    --ws-terracotta: #E8653A;
    --ws-sage: #2D5A3D;
    --ws-grey: #6B7280;
    --ws-light-grey: #E5E2DD;
    --ws-font-display: 'DM Serif Display', Georgia, serif;
    --ws-font-body: 'DM Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;
  }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    font-family: var(--ws-font-body);
    color: var(--ws-black);
    background: var(--ws-white);
    line-height: 1.65;
    font-size: 16px;
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  }

  .ws-container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  /* --- NAV --- */
  .ws-nav {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    background: rgba(250, 250, 248, 0.92);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ws-light-grey);
  }

  .ws-nav-inner {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    height: 72px;
  }

  .ws-logo {
    font-family: var(--ws-font-display);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--ws-black);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .ws-nav-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .ws-nav-links a {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--ws-grey);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 200ms ease;
  }

  .ws-nav-links a:hover { color: var(--ws-terracotta); }

  .ws-nav-cta { font-size: 0.85rem !important; padding: 0.5rem 1.25rem !important; }

  /* --- BUTTONS --- */
  .ws-btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    font-family: var(--ws-font-body);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    padding: 0.85rem 1.75rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 250ms cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
    cursor: pointer;
    border: none;
  }

  .ws-btn-primary {
    background: var(--ws-terracotta);
    color: white;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(232, 101, 58, 0.25);
  }

  .ws-btn-primary:hover {
    background: #d4562e;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(232, 101, 58, 0.35);
  }

  .ws-btn-ghost {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--ws-black);
    border: 1.5px solid var(--ws-light-grey);
  }

  .ws-btn-ghost:hover {
    border-color: var(--ws-terracotta);
    color: var(--ws-terracotta);
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }

  .ws-btn-lg { font-size: 1.05rem; padding: 1rem 2.25rem; }

  /* --- HERO --- */
  .ws-hero {
    position: relative;
    padding: 10rem 0 7rem;
    background: var(--ws-white);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .ws-hero-grain {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    opacity: 0.35;
    background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 256 256' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='noise'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.9' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23noise)' opacity='0.04'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .ws-hero-dot-grid {
    position: absolute;
    top: 15%;
    right: 5%;
    width: 240px;
    height: 240px;
    background-image: radial-gradient(circle, var(--ws-terracotta) 1.2px, transparent 1.2px);
    background-size: 20px 20px;
    opacity: 0.12;
    animation: ws-drift 20s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes ws-drift {
    0%, 100% { transform: translate(0, 0); }
    50% { transform: translate(-10px, 10px); }
  }

  .ws-hero-content {
    max-width: 680px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .ws-overline {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ws-sage);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .ws-hero h1 {
    font-family: var(--ws-font-display);
    font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 6vw, 4.5rem);
    line-height: 1.1;
    color: var(--ws-black);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .ws-accent { color: var(--ws-terracotta); }

  .ws-hero-sub {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: var(--ws-grey);
    max-width: 540px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .ws-hero-actions { display: flex; gap: 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }

  /* --- SECTIONS --- */
  .ws-section { padding: 6rem 0; }
  .ws-section-white { background: var(--ws-white); }
  .ws-section-cream { background: var(--ws-cream); }

  .ws-section-title {
    font-family: var(--ws-font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.5rem);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--ws-black);
  }

  .ws-section-subtitle {
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--ws-grey);
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto 3.5rem;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }

  /* --- BENEFITS GRID --- */
  .ws-benefits-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 3.5rem;
  }

  .ws-benefit-card {
    background: var(--ws-white);
    border: 1px solid var(--ws-light-grey);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 2rem;
    transition: all 300ms cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
  }

  .ws-benefit-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.08);
    border-color: transparent;
  }

  .ws-benefit-icon {
    width: 52px;
    height: 52px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .ws-icon-terracotta { background: rgba(232, 101, 58, 0.1); color: var(--ws-terracotta); }
  .ws-icon-sage { background: rgba(45, 90, 61, 0.1); color: var(--ws-sage); }

  .ws-benefit-card h3 {
    font-family: var(--ws-font-display);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .ws-benefit-card p {
    color: var(--ws-grey);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* --- TESTIMONIAL --- */
  .ws-testimonial-strip {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 720px;
  }

  .ws-testimonial-strip blockquote p {
    font-family: var(--ws-font-display);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--ws-black);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .ws-testimonial-strip cite {
    font-style: normal;
    color: var(--ws-grey);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  /* --- USE CASES --- */
  .ws-use-cases {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 3.5rem;
  }

  .ws-use-card {
    background: var(--ws-white);
    border: 1px solid var(--ws-light-grey);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
    transition: all 300ms cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
    position: relative;
  }

  .ws-use-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.08);
  }

  .ws-use-number {
    font-family: var(--ws-font-display);
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: var(--ws-terracotta);
    opacity: 0.2;
    position: absolute;
    top: 1.25rem;
    right: 1.5rem;
  }

  .ws-use-card h3 {
    font-family: var(--ws-font-display);
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .ws-use-card p { color: var(--ws-grey); font-size: 0.95rem; }

  /* --- JOURNEY --- */
  .ws-journey {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0;
    margin-top: 3.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .ws-journey-step {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 180px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .ws-step-marker {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--ws-terracotta);
    color: white;
